cast.overview: The story of a precocious six year-old and her ragtag group of friends whose summer break is filled with childhood wonder, possibility and a sense of adventure while the adults around them struggle with hard times.
cast.title: The Florida Project

details.biography: Valeria Cotto (born on September 30, 2010) is an American actress and filmmaker from Orlando, Florida. Her breakout role was in Sean Baker’s The Florida Project (2017). She is also known for the Backup Plan (2019), Over/Under (2022) and Paper Tiger (2025).
details.name: Valeria Cotto
